project.name: Nameday api and opensource library
project.description: This [opensource library](https://github.com/xnekv03/nameday-api) acts as client for [Nameday API](https://nameday.abalin.net) which is developed and maintained by me in my free time since 2017. Library is opensource and API is for free serving 60 000 requests a day. Namday is providing data for 20 countries.
